{
  "video_id": "21hgbMa_sVc",
  "title": "How farming could employ Africa's young workforce -- and help build peace | Kola Masha",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12904.0,
      "end_time": 17786.0,
      "text": "Since 1997, researchers at the University of Sussex"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17810.0,
      "end_time": 21900.0,
      "text": "have monitored global trends in armed conflict."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21863.0,
      "end_time": 25430.0,
      "text": "Their research clearly shows"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 25670.0,
      "end_time": 28871.0,
      "text": "that in Africa, over the last 10 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 28895.0,
      "end_time": 32576.0,
      "text": "armed conflict has gone up by sevenfold."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 32927.0,
      "end_time": 34460.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s think about that:"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34847.0,
      "end_time": 38690.0,
      "text": "sevenfold in a single decade."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 40622.0,
      "end_time": 41772.0,
      "text": "Why is this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 42829.0,
      "end_time": 46162.0,
      "text": "We believe, as oxygen is to fire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 46186.0,
      "end_time": 49495.0,
      "text": "so are unemployed youth to insecurity."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 50546.0,
      "end_time": 54305.0,
      "text": "We have a lot of youth on this continent."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 54791.0,
      "end_time": 56733.0,
      "text": "Youth like Sandra,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 57829.0,
      "end_time": 62839.0,
      "text": "who, on a Saturday morning in March 2014,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 62863.0,
      "end_time": 67120.0,
      "text": "woke up excited at the prospects of getting a coveted job"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 67144.0,
      "end_time": 69716.0,
      "text": "at the Nigerian Immigration Services."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 70263.0,
      "end_time": 73820.0,
      "text": "She kissed her daughter goodbye,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 73106.0,
      "end_time": 74381.0,
      "text": "left her home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 75820.0,
      "end_time": 76238.0,
      "text": "never to return."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 76632.0,
      "end_time": 82877.0,
      "text": "Sandra and 15 other young Nigerians died that day, applying for a job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 84942.0,
      "end_time": 86723.0,
      "text": "in the ensuing stampede,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 87601.0,
      "end_time": 93887.0,
      "text": "as tens of thousands of people applied for a few thousand open positions."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 98431.0,
      "end_time": 104899.0,
      "text": "In the last 20 years, 20 million youth have entered the Nigerian workforce alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 105939.0,
      "end_time": 111723.0,
      "text": "Today, half our population is under the age of 18."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 112164.0,
      "end_time": 115410.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s almost 80 million people"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 115434.0,
      "end_time": 119301.0,
      "text": "that will be entering the workforce in the next 20 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 121421.0,
      "end_time": 123398.0,
      "text": "My friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 123422.0,
      "end_time": 128413.0,
      "text": "if a wave of 20 million people entering the workforce"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 128437.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130916.00000000001,
      "text": "triggered Niger Delta crisis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 131768.0,
      "end_time": 134370.0,
      "text": "Fulani herdsmen crisis"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 134610.0,
      "end_time": 135808.0,
      "text": "and Boko Haram,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 136768.0,
      "end_time": 138169.0,
      "text": "I ask you:"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 138193.0,
      "end_time": 141453.0,
      "text": "What will four times that number do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 143614.0,
      "end_time": 146955.0,
      "text": "To do my part to solve this challenge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 146979.0,
      "end_time": 151301.0,
      "text": "in 2012, I moved to a small village in northern Nigeria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 152507.0,
      "end_time": 156994.0,
      "text": "in the center of the area most recently hit"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 157180.0,
      "end_time": 163696.0,
      "text": "by the spread of insecurity, brutal bombings and searing poverty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 163720.0,
      "end_time": 165290.0,
      "text": "with an idea:"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 166522.0,
      "end_time": 173196.0,
      "text": "Could we create an economic buffer to halt the spread of this insecurity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 173220.0,
      "end_time": 177185.0,
      "text": "by unlocking the power of agriculture as a job-creation engine?"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 178850.0,
      "end_time": 182690.0,
      "text": "We knew this had been done before in countries like Thailand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 182930.0,
      "end_time": 186399.0,
      "text": "where, in 1980, they suffered from the same economic challenges as us."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 187577.0,
      "end_time": 192981.0,
      "text": "Today, however, Thailand produces two million cars a year --"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 193500.0,
      "end_time": 195513.0,
      "text": "more than the United Kingdom --"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 195537.0,
      "end_time": 198403.0,
      "text": "with over 30 percent of its workforce"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 198427.0,
      "end_time": 201958.0,
      "text": "as highly commercial, profitable small farmers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 202633.0,
      "end_time": 208930.0,
      "text": "with an unemployment rate of less than one percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 209793.0,
      "end_time": 211193.0,
      "text": "How did they do this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 211690.0,
      "end_time": 217323.0,
      "text": "In the 80s, Thailand dramatically improved the productivity of its small farmers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 219543.0,
      "end_time": 224141.0,
      "text": "ensuring that it was able to start to dominate"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 224165.0,
      "end_time": 226156.0,
      "text": "export markets for produce."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 227141.0,
      "end_time": 229855.0,
      "text": "Building on this strength, they attracted investment"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 229879.0,
      "end_time": 232220.0,
      "text": "and started to process,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 232244.0,
      "end_time": 236260.0,
      "text": "being able to export higher-value products like starch from cassava."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 237220.0,
      "end_time": 240315.0,
      "text": "Finally, coupled with investment in education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 240339.0,
      "end_time": 244497.0,
      "text": "they started to expand to even higher-value manufacturing."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 246966.0,
      "end_time": 252283.0,
      "text": "To make our idea a reality and follow a path similar to Thailand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 252307.0,
      "end_time": 258700.0,
      "text": "we knew that we would have to sell young farmers on farming."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 260125.0,
      "end_time": 262954.0,
      "text": "A young man in northern Nigeria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 262978.0,
      "end_time": 267442.0,
      "text": "for the purpose of today&#39;s discussion, we&#39;ll call \"Saminu,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 267466.0,
      "end_time": 270442.0,
      "text": "made it very clear to me that this would not be easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 271363.0,
      "end_time": 275960.0,
      "text": "Saminu grew up in a beautiful village in northern Nigeria."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 275571.0,
      "end_time": 279627.0,
      "text": "And he tells wondrous stories of playing for hours with his friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 279651.0,
      "end_time": 282120.0,
      "text": "running up and down the beautiful rock formations"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 282144.0,
      "end_time": 284877.0,
      "text": "that dot the countryside around his home."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 285839.0,
      "end_time": 288395.0,
      "text": "Despite this beauty, Saminu knew"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 288419.0,
      "end_time": 291140.0,
      "text": "that the first chance he got, he would leave."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 292315.0,
      "end_time": 294283.0,
      "text": "He did not want to be a farmer."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 295431.0,
      "end_time": 300835.0,
      "text": "Growing up, he saw his parents work so hard as farmers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 300860.0,
      "end_time": 302843.0,
      "text": "but barely get by."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 303934.0,
      "end_time": 308339.0,
      "text": "As he says, they had \"babu\" -- nothing."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 311266.0,
      "end_time": 315885.0,
      "text": "Young farmers like Saminu"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 315909.0,
      "end_time": 318607.0,
      "text": "do not have access to the cash"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 318631.0,
      "end_time": 322580.0,
      "text": "to buy the farming products to pair with their hard work"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 322820.0,
      "end_time": 323882.0,
      "text": "to be successful."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 326462.0,
      "end_time": 328287.0,
      "text": "When their meager harvest came in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 328311.0,
      "end_time": 333570.0,
      "text": "desperate for cash, they would sell most of it at fire-sale prices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 333594.0,
      "end_time": 337724.0,
      "text": "when, if they could just wait six months, they could get 50 percent more."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 338538.0,
      "end_time": 342795.0,
      "text": "Hence, Saminu left to the city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 344180.0,
      "end_time": 347314.0,
      "text": "where he soon realized that life was not easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 348236.0,
      "end_time": 351301.0,
      "text": "He borrowed a very old motorcycle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 352276.0,
      "end_time": 355815.0,
      "text": "with tires that were more patches than tires,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 355839.0,
      "end_time": 358290.0,
      "text": "to become a motorcycle taxi driver."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 359553.0,
      "end_time": 363450.0,
      "text": "He lived in constant fear every day"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 363690.0,
      "end_time": 367887.0,
      "text": "that his precious, tattered motorcycle would be ripped away from him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 367911.0,
      "end_time": 369763.0,
      "text": "as it had before."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 371934.0,
      "end_time": 374806.0,
      "text": "But he got it back, thankfully."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 376315.0,
      "end_time": 378997.0,
      "text": "He knew of others, however, who were not so lucky --"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 379617.0,
      "end_time": 382323.0,
      "text": "other young men who, once they&#39;d lost their motorcycles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 382347.0,
      "end_time": 383704.0,
      "text": "became destitute."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 385268.0,
      "end_time": 388164.0,
      "text": "Angry, these young men set out to wreak vengeance"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 388189.0,
      "end_time": 392180.0,
      "text": "on a society that they believed had turned its back on them."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 394617.0,
      "end_time": 400529.0,
      "text": "Saminu told me that they joined insurgent groups,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 400553.0,
      "end_time": 405537.0,
      "text": "often acting as getaway drivers in bombings and kidnappings."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 407140.0,
      "end_time": 410765.0,
      "text": "To end this cycle of insecurity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 410790.0,
      "end_time": 413854.0,
      "text": "we must make farming a viable choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 413878.0,
      "end_time": 417760.0,
      "text": "We must ensure that these young men, on their small farms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 417784.0,
      "end_time": 421577.0,
      "text": "can earn enough money to make a life for themselves;"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 421601.0,
      "end_time": 422751.0,
      "text": "to make a future."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 423323.0,
      "end_time": 425561.0,
      "text": "The question now is how."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 426315.0,
      "end_time": 430180.0,
      "text": "Recognizing that Africa has grassroot-level leadership,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 430204.0,
      "end_time": 432847.0,
      "text": "we simply developed a model"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 432871.0,
      "end_time": 436306.0,
      "text": "to bring the professional management and investment to scale"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 436331.0,
      "end_time": 439104.0,
      "text": "to these grassroot leaders."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 440600.0,
      "end_time": 445152.0,
      "text": "We called it \"Babban Gona\" -- \"great farm\" in Hausa."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 446948.0,
      "end_time": 451519.0,
      "text": "Upon reaching the village in 2012,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 451543.0,
      "end_time": 453805.0,
      "text": "I traveled from community to community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 453829.0,
      "end_time": 457686.0,
      "text": "trying to convince people of our idea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 458152.0,
      "end_time": 462534.0,
      "text": "trying to recruit farmer members."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 463319.0,
      "end_time": 466115.0,
      "text": "We failed woefully that first year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 466895.0,
      "end_time": 469775.0,
      "text": "barely recruiting 100 brave souls."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 471530.0,
      "end_time": 472253.0,
      "text": "But we persevered."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 472990.0,
      "end_time": 476196.0,
      "text": "We kept doing what we promised,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 476220.0,
      "end_time": 479874.0,
      "text": "slowly we gained their trust."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 482380.0,
      "end_time": 483571.0,
      "text": "More farmers joined us."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 484315.0,
      "end_time": 486353.0,
      "text": "Fast-forward now five years."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 486377.0,
      "end_time": 488739.0,
      "text": "With a passionate and committed team"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 490165.0,
      "end_time": 493259.0,
      "text": "and the tremendous support of our partners,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 494695.0,
      "end_time": 496940.0,
      "text": "we grew dramatically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 497509.0,
      "end_time": 501457.0,
      "text": "today, serving 20,000 small farmers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 501481.0,
      "end_time": 508396.0,
      "text": "enabling them to double their yields and triple their net income"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 508420.0,
      "end_time": 509902.0,
      "text": "relative to their peers."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 511552.0,
      "end_time": 513649.0,
      "text": "We are very proud of the fact --"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 513673.0,
      "end_time": 518696.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 518720.0,
      "end_time": 520918.0,
      "text": "Fast-forward three years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 520942.0,
      "end_time": 522506.0,
      "text": "Saminu has earned enough money"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 522530.0,
      "end_time": 527227.0,
      "text": "to buy three goats for his mother to start a goat-rearing business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 527251.0,
      "end_time": 530164.0,
      "text": "owns his own retail store"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 530188.0,
      "end_time": 535473.0,
      "text": "and bought not one, but two motorcycles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 535498.0,
      "end_time": 538966.0,
      "text": "with vanity license plates: \"Babban Gona.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 538990.0,
      "end_time": 544370.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 544956.0,
      "end_time": 546126.0,
      "text": "My friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 547322.0,
      "end_time": 548840.0,
      "text": "in the next 20 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 549702.0,
      "end_time": 554300.0,
      "text": "over 400 million Saminus are entering the African workforce,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 554855.0,
      "end_time": 558988.0,
      "text": "with potentially half of them having opportunities in agriculture."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 559704.0,
      "end_time": 564635.0,
      "text": "To unlock these opportunities, through models similar to ours,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 564659.0,
      "end_time": 570231.0,
      "text": "they would require 150 billion dollars a year in financing."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 572260.0,
      "end_time": 573425.0,
      "text": "This is a big number."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 574278.0,
      "end_time": 579724.0,
      "text": "But if we can tap into commercial debt, it is a small number --"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 579748.0,
      "end_time": 583663.0,
      "text": "only 0.1 percent of all the debt in the world today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 583687.0,
      "end_time": 586728.0,
      "text": "10 cents out of every 100 dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 587347.0,
      "end_time": 589266.0,
      "text": "This is why we designed our model"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 589290.0,
      "end_time": 593400.0,
      "text": "to be very different from conventional agricultural development programs."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 593363.0,
      "end_time": 598607.0,
      "text": "In a few short years, we have shown that our model works,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 598631.0,
      "end_time": 602416.0,
      "text": "is high-impact and can turn a profit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 602441.0,
      "end_time": 604117.0,
      "text": "attracting commercial investors"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 604141.0,
      "end_time": 608820.0,
      "text": "that do not typically invest in small farmers in Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 609807.0,
      "end_time": 615450.0,
      "text": "Imagine a world where millions of young men across Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 615690.0,
      "end_time": 617299.0,
      "text": "hardworking young men,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 617323.0,
      "end_time": 618807.0,
      "text": "have other options."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 619998.0,
      "end_time": 625650.0,
      "text": "I know these driven, ambitious young men"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 626590.0,
      "end_time": 628597.0,
      "text": "will make the right choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 631990.0,
      "end_time": 634477.0,
      "text": "We can realize this dream"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 636268.0,
      "end_time": 640353.0,
      "text": "if they have a choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 641172.0,
      "end_time": 642324.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 642348.0,
      "end_time": 646246.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}